# Chapter 6: Time Table

The **Time Table** module provides a weekly calendar view of all doctors' schedules, showing their available session times for each day. It helps staff quickly see when each doctor is available and manage scheduling. Access it by clicking **Time Table** in the left sidebar.

---

## 6.1 Time Table Screen Overview

The screen displays a **weekly grid** titled **Doctors Time Table**, with doctors listed as rows and days of the week as columns.

---

## 6.2 Week Navigation

At the top of the screen:

| Button | Action |
|---|---|
| **◀ Previous Week** | Moves the calendar back to the previous week |
| **Next Week ▶** | Moves the calendar forward to the next week |

The column headers show each day of the week with its full date (e.g., *Sunday 19-04-2026*, *Monday 20-04-2026*, etc.), so you always know exactly which dates you are viewing.

---

