# Chapter 12: Administration

The **Administration** module is the control centre for the entire Acvilas system. It is where administrators configure the clinic's setup, manage staff access, define services, control stock, and manage system-wide settings. Access it by clicking **Administration** (the wrench/settings icon) in the left sidebar.

---

## 12.1 Administration Home

The Administration home page is titled **Administration** with the subtitle *"Manage your clinical ecosystem and system configurations."*

It displays **12 configuration modules** arranged in a grid of colourful cards. Each card leads to a dedicated settings area:

---

## 12.2 Administration Modules Overview

### Row 1

| Card | Colour | Purpose |
