# Chapter 12.1: Administration — Doctors

The **Doctors** section under Administration is where all doctor profiles are created and managed. This includes their personal details, consultation fees, schedules, and booking settings. Access it from **Administration > Doctors**.

---

## 12.1.1 Doctors List Screen

The screen is titled **Administration > Doctors** and displays all registered doctors in the system.

At the top:
- **Search by name** — Type to filter the doctor list by name
- **Refresh** — Reloads the list
- **+ New Doctor** — Opens the form to create a new doctor profile (top right, dark button)

