---

## 12.1.2 Viewing Doctor Details

Click **Details** in the Options column to open the doctor's profile popup. This displays a read-only summary of all configured settings:

### Doctor Section
- **Name** — Doctor's full name
- **Tagline** — Doctor's title/specialisation

### Charges Section
- **Doctor Charge** — The portion of the consultation fee that goes to the doctor
- **Hospital Charge** — The portion that goes to the hospital/clinic

