## 12.1.3 Editing a Doctor Profile

Click **Edit Details** from the Details popup, or click **Details > Edit Details** to open the **Edit Doctor** form. All fields are editable:

| Field | Description |
|---|---|
| **Change Image** | Click to upload a new profile photo for the doctor |
| **Doctor Name** | The doctor's full name |
| **Title** | Specialisation or role title |
| **Doctor Charge** | Fee amount allocated to the doctor |
| **Hospital Charge** | Fee amount allocated to the hospital/clinic |
| **Charge Type** | Dropdown — *Before Meet* (payment collected before consultation) or *After Meet* |
| **Waiting List Index By** | Dropdown — *App ID* (orders waiting list by appointment ID) or *Bill ID* |
| **SMS Notification** | Dropdown — *Enable* or *Disable* SMS alerts for this doctor's appointments |
| **Enable Online Booking** | Dropdown — *Active* (patients can book online) or *Disable* |
