2. Enter the **Doctor Name** and **Title**.
3. Set the **Doctor Charge** and **Hospital Charge** amounts.
4. Choose the **Charge Type** — *Before Meet* or *After Meet*.
5. Set **SMS Notification** — *Enable* or *Disable*.
6. Set **Waiting List Index By** — *Bill ID* or *App ID*.
7. Set **Enable Online Booking** — *Active* or *Disable*.
