1. Click **+ New Note** (dark button, top right of the popup).
2. Enter the date and the note content.
3. Save the note.

> ⚠️ **Important:** Notes added here will **appear as an alert when an appointment is being booked** for this doctor on or around that date. Use this feature to warn booking staff about schedule changes, doctor unavailability, public holidays, or any special instructions relevant to that date.

